<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.3.6">
<l>vaittā raṭiyār maṉattiṉil vaittiṉpam</l>
<l>uyttā roḷivicumpi lōraṭivait tōraṭikkum</l>
<l>eyttātu maṇṇeṉ ṟimaiyōr toḻutiṟaiñci</l>
<l>kaittā maraikuvikkuṅ kaṇṇaṉeṉ kaṇṇaṉaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In [their] minds, devotees keep [him]; keeping [him], they relish delight.</l>
<l>The celestials join their lotus palms, saying,</l>
<l>“Keeping one foot in the radiant sky,</l>
<l rend="indent">the earth is not enough for another foot,”</l>
<l>Worshipping and bowing low to Kaṇṇaṉ, my Kaṇṇaṉ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
